Text: 'Let Me Roll It' has a 'Foxy Lady' Hendrix jam in it.
Download my pics from the second night in Orlando.  They are up to par with others that I've seen from professional photographers.

There are some pretty huge explosions of pyro during 'Live and Let Die'.  It actually accents the tune really well and makes it more powerful.  When I was there, they sounded like huge bombs going off simultaneously.  

I can't say enough praises of his Orlando performances each night!
I don't know if the folks who grab these torrents know how much work goes into it.  A "Thanks" is always appreciated.
